Seq3.CallerContent: Good morning. This is Brian Fryer. I'm calling to find out the status of my wife's referral being processed to TRICARE. If you can call me back, my number is 443-634-2954. Thank you.
Seq3.ReceiverContent: Hello. You have reached the receptionist at Crofton Family Practice. Please leave your name, reason for calling, and your number so we can call you back as soon as we can. If you are experiencing a medical emergency, please hang up and dial 911. If you are calling after hours or on weekends, we have an answering service that you can call if you think this is an urgent matter that the physician needs to address. You can call that. We have an answering service number at 443-481-1000. Thanks for calling.
